{"tid":1517894,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有冇諗過政府唔批遊行集會都係想分化我地？","createTime":"2019-08-30T05:15:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T05:28:01.000Z","uid":102775,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e54e1f867482d2d4d8c34997bb1bd6e071f404a","tid":1517894,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:15:33.000Z","msg":"聽日出左分對通知書一定會少左好多唔想冒險出黎嘅人，到時會因爲少左人而變得多左機會比狗拉。<br />\n如果出現呢個情況實會有人話點解明知有反對通知書仲要出 ，出左嘅就指責返冇出黎嘅人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結論係我地聽日點都要團結一致一齊出，等政府呢招無效化！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不割席 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uc7J0Uk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuc7J0Uk.jpg&h=01aa7b6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"854cf48678e4a5ee88b599c6db6ef9a1d8522013","tid":1517894,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8mCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=9a009927\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8mCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=f300cc8b\" target=\"_blank\">ht